00:30:44.680 --> 00:30:48.040 align:middle line:84%
by 2029, all of us,
within our pockets,

00:30:48.040 --> 00:30:51.707 align:middle line:84%
will have our own personalized
artificial intelligence.

00:30:51.707 --> 00:30:54.040 align:middle line:84%
