of relationships,

00:34:02.410 --> 00:34:04.950 align:middle line:84%
new definitions of
love, by teaching them

00:34:04.950 --> 00:34:07.290 align:middle line:84%
that the dogma of
organized religion

00:34:07.290 --> 00:34:10.170 align:middle line:84%
can often create
pain and setback

00:34:10.170 --> 00:34:12.415 align:middle line:84%
and to teach them new
models of spirituality,

00:34:12.415 --> 00:34:14.790 align:middle line:84%
to teach them creativity, to
teach them entrepreneurship,

00:34:14.790 --> 00:34:16.440 align:middle line:84%
to teach them that
love doesn't have

00:34:16.440 --> 00:34:17.850 align:middle line:90%
to come from outside forces--

00:34:17.850 --> 00:34:19.620 align:middle line:90%
it can be generated within--

00:34:19.620 --> 00:34:22.574 align:middle line:84%
that you are enough as
you are, no matter what

00:34:22.574 --> 00:34:24.449 align:middle line:84%
